1
00:00:36,110 --> 00:00:41,240
♪In rain or shine♪

2
00:00:41,780 --> 00:00:46,870
♪When you're around,
the sun shines through♪

3
00:00:47,220 --> 00:00:52,640
♪Spare ourselves the endless thoughts
and guessing games♪

4
00:00:52,930 --> 00:00:58,880
♪Let's just meet
and escape these frames♪

5
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:02,600
♪I stand within the shadows deep♪

6
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:08,030
♪My hand outstretched,
your rescue I keep♪

7
00:01:08,220 --> 00:01:12,850
♪Even if the world falls apart♪

8
00:01:13,170 --> 00:01:15,870
♪No distance is too far♪

9
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:21,390
♪To stop us from coming together♪

10
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:27,710
♪Through the night,
you're at the end of the line♪

11
00:01:28,710 --> 00:01:32,730
♪To protect you is my humble wish♪

12
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:36,920
♪Farewell, to the timid soul I knew♪

13
00:01:37,270 --> 00:01:42,550
♪It was you who made me brave and new♪

14
00:01:42,550 --> 00:01:46,180
=Always Home=
(Adapted from Xiao Ge's novel, Always Home)

15
00:01:46,260 --> 00:01:49,180
=Episode 6=
(One, Two, Three, Pinocchio)

16
00:01:49,940 --> 00:01:50,870
Qi Qi.

17
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:52,780
Qi Qi.

18
00:01:57,550 --> 00:01:58,620
This is for you.

19
00:01:59,790 --> 00:02:00,780
Surprised?

20
00:02:01,510 --> 00:02:03,670
This is a gift from the three of us.

21
00:02:04,460 --> 00:02:05,390
Qi Qi,

22
00:02:05,550 --> 00:02:07,949
we hope you can freely

23
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:09,780
pursue what you love.

24
00:02:16,580 --> 00:02:18,870
The video was your idea, right?

25
00:02:19,390 --> 00:02:20,710
That wasn't me.

26
00:02:20,780 --> 00:02:22,229
That was Jing Xichi.

27
00:02:22,230 --> 00:02:23,940
He did all the editing and video work.

28
00:02:24,340 --> 00:02:25,890
Didn't I tell you not to say that?

29
00:02:25,900 --> 00:02:27,340
Don't be so modest.

30
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:32,520
The bakery said they couldn't make
a big cake in time.

31
00:02:32,540 --> 00:02:34,500
This one is small,
but it's really delicious.

32
00:02:36,270 --> 00:02:37,220
Thank you.

33
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,550
Editing the video must've been tough.

34
00:02:41,340 --> 00:02:42,710
Also...

35
00:02:43,950 --> 00:02:45,549
I didn't understand.

36
00:02:45,550 --> 00:02:46,900
I shouldn't have said that.

37
00:02:47,550 --> 00:02:50,550
You'll definitely get better
and better at soccer.

38
00:02:51,430 --> 00:02:52,660
You'll reach your dream.

39
00:02:54,620 --> 00:02:56,100
I've already forgotten about it.

40
00:03:02,950 --> 00:03:05,030
Thank you all so much.

41
00:03:06,340 --> 00:03:07,310
Don't mention it.

42
00:03:10,500 --> 00:03:11,550
Qi Qi,

43
00:03:12,550 --> 00:03:13,500
how about a hug?

44
00:03:15,740 --> 00:03:16,779
Let me hold that for you.

45
00:03:16,780 --> 00:03:18,470
You two hug.

46
00:03:20,340 --> 00:03:21,340
Qi Qi,

47
00:03:21,870 --> 00:03:24,150
don't forget me
after you transfer classes.

48
00:03:24,180 --> 00:03:25,179
I won't.

49
00:03:25,180 --> 00:03:27,430
I'll never forget you.

50
00:03:28,580 --> 00:03:30,380
You mustn't forget me.

51
00:03:31,300 --> 00:03:33,100
I'll never forget you.

52
00:03:34,230 --> 00:03:34,990
No crying.

53
00:03:35,990 --> 00:03:37,500
Alright, alright.

54
00:03:40,550 --> 00:03:42,310
I won't forget you guys either.

55
00:03:45,230 --> 00:03:46,870
Let's have a hug too.

56
00:03:48,740 --> 00:03:50,470
After all, we're parting ways.

57
00:04:11,780 --> 00:04:12,750
Thank you.

58
00:04:15,270 --> 00:04:16,100
It's nothing.

59
00:04:16,620 --> 00:04:17,299
It's no big deal.

60
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:18,620
I'll get going now.

61
00:04:18,790 --> 00:04:19,259
Alright.

62
00:04:19,260 --> 00:04:20,619
Text me when you get home.

63
00:04:20,620 --> 00:04:21,550
Don't mention it.

64
00:04:22,140 --> 00:04:22,549
Bye-bye.

65
00:04:22,550 --> 00:04:23,179
I'll get going.

66
00:04:23,180 --> 00:04:23,909
Bye-bye.

67
00:04:23,910 --> 00:04:24,820
Bye-bye.

68
00:04:25,260 --> 00:04:26,990
Be careful on your way home.

69
00:04:55,740 --> 00:04:57,670
You're pretty good with computers.

70
00:04:57,700 --> 00:04:59,379
I never thought about it before.

71
00:04:59,380 --> 00:05:00,669
I always thought

72
00:05:00,670 --> 00:05:02,139
that you couldn't do anything else

73
00:05:02,140 --> 00:05:03,550
besides playing soccer.

74
00:05:04,430 --> 00:05:05,259
Well, it depends

75
00:05:05,260 --> 00:05:06,740
on whether I actually want to do it.

76
00:05:06,740 --> 00:05:07,860
If I don't do something well,

77
00:05:07,870 --> 00:05:09,990
it's simply because I'm not interested.

78
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:21,229
You don't want Qi Qi to transfer,

79
00:05:21,230 --> 00:05:22,430
do you?

80
00:05:24,910 --> 00:05:26,310
Why are you suddenly asking this?

81
00:05:27,300 --> 00:05:29,620
Nothing, I just feel like

82
00:05:30,140 --> 00:05:31,820
you treat Qi Qi differently.

83
00:05:36,550 --> 00:05:38,580
Once Qi Qi transfers
to the humanities class,

84
00:05:38,700 --> 00:05:40,580
stop deliberately doing poorly in exams.

85
00:06:10,740 --> 00:06:11,139
Hello.

86
00:06:11,140 --> 00:06:11,739
Huan'er?

87
00:06:11,740 --> 00:06:12,430
Qi Qi,

88
00:06:12,670 --> 00:06:14,589
did you see the field trip info

89
00:06:14,590 --> 00:06:15,460
I sent you?

90
00:06:15,790 --> 00:06:16,620
Yeah, I saw it.

91
00:06:17,300 --> 00:06:18,670
I really want to go,

92
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,090
but my mom definitely won't let me.

93
00:06:20,180 --> 00:06:20,909
She just told me

94
00:06:20,910 --> 00:06:22,870
I have a bunch of tutoring classes
in the summer.

95
00:06:24,300 --> 00:06:26,059
But it's school break.

96
00:06:26,060 --> 00:06:27,550
Why won't she let you go?

97
00:06:27,790 --> 00:06:29,029
It's not just a trip.

98
00:06:29,030 --> 00:06:30,179
It's an educational trip.

99
00:06:30,180 --> 00:06:31,349
We'll visit museums

100
00:06:31,350 --> 00:06:32,910
to learn.

101
00:06:33,110 --> 00:06:34,299
Besides, everyone's going.

102
00:06:34,300 --> 00:06:35,869
Me, Jing Xichi,

103
00:06:35,870 --> 00:06:38,140
Xinyan, Song Cong... everyone.

104
00:06:38,430 --> 00:06:39,110
Are you going?

105
00:06:39,590 --> 00:06:41,020
Liao Xinyan is going too?

106
00:06:41,350 --> 00:06:42,110
Yeah.

107
00:06:43,110 --> 00:06:43,940
Are you going?

108
00:06:47,820 --> 00:06:49,790
I probably won't be able to go.

109
00:06:53,470 --> 00:06:54,350
Alright then.

110
00:06:54,740 --> 00:06:55,460
Bye-bye.

111
00:07:06,550 --> 00:07:07,460
How much?

112
00:07:07,590 --> 00:07:08,350
Ten yuan.

113
00:07:08,820 --> 00:07:09,380
Here.

114
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:21,989
Hey,

115
00:07:21,990 --> 00:07:23,580
you two didn't wait for me.

116
00:07:24,620 --> 00:07:25,179
Huan'er.

117
00:07:25,180 --> 00:07:26,110
Xinyan!

118
00:07:28,100 --> 00:07:29,580
I didn't see you the entire break.

119
00:07:29,590 --> 00:07:31,230
I kept asking you out. Where were you?

120
00:07:32,020 --> 00:07:33,870
I went back to my hometown
for a few days.

121
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,810
I talked to the group leader earlier.

122
00:07:38,820 --> 00:07:39,789
We're sharing a room.

123
00:07:39,790 --> 00:07:41,140
We can have a nice chat tonight.

124
00:07:41,940 --> 00:07:42,990
This is really good.

125
00:07:44,260 --> 00:07:45,060
Huan'er.

126
00:07:46,740 --> 00:07:47,820
Qi Qi?

127
00:07:48,300 --> 00:07:49,550
You signed up?

128
00:07:49,910 --> 00:07:51,589
I thought you weren't coming.

129
00:07:51,590 --> 00:07:52,299
Yeah, I signed up.

130
00:07:52,300 --> 00:07:54,200
I signed up the day
after you told me about it.

131
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:56,480
I was worried I might not make it,
so I didn't tell you.

132
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:57,290
That's amazing.

133
00:07:57,300 --> 00:07:58,700
How did you convince your mom?

134
00:07:59,550 --> 00:08:01,620
I have my ways.

135
00:08:02,740 --> 00:08:03,620
This is great.

136
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:05,230
Looks like everyone is here now.

137
00:08:05,430 --> 00:08:06,910
Driver, let's go.

138
00:08:07,260 --> 00:08:08,699
The bus is leaving, sit down.

139
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:09,660
Xinyan, I wanted to...

140
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,500
Sit down...

141
00:08:10,740 --> 00:08:11,869
We'll talk later.

142
00:08:11,870 --> 00:08:12,379
Okay.

143
00:08:12,380 --> 00:08:13,139
Sit down.

144
00:08:13,140 --> 00:08:13,790
Okay.

145
00:08:17,030 --> 00:08:17,909
Jing Xichi.

146
00:08:17,910 --> 00:08:19,819
You should be the class monitor
for this trip.

147
00:08:19,820 --> 00:08:21,299
You're really good at organizing.

148
00:08:21,300 --> 00:08:22,299
No way.

149
00:08:22,300 --> 00:08:23,260
Let Song Cong do it.

150
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:44,130
Alright, students, get off the bus.

151
00:08:44,140 --> 00:08:45,100
Grab your luggage.

152
00:08:46,740 --> 00:08:48,019
You still haven't told me

153
00:08:48,020 --> 00:08:49,740
how you convince your mom.

154
00:08:49,870 --> 00:08:50,739
Me?

155
00:08:50,740 --> 00:08:52,189
I told my mom

156
00:08:52,190 --> 00:08:54,420
that I'm going on an educational tour
with classmates,

157
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,580
that it's for learning,

158
00:08:55,590 --> 00:08:56,739
not for fun.

159
00:08:56,740 --> 00:08:57,409
Huan'er.

160
00:08:57,410 --> 00:08:59,590
Can I borrow some
of mosquito repellent you were using?

161
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,820
That's Qi Qi's.

162
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:01,709
Qi Qi,

163
00:09:01,710 --> 00:09:04,100
can you share your mosquito repellent
with Xinyan?

164
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:11,220
Thanks.

165
00:09:14,660 --> 00:09:15,539
Xinyan,

166
00:09:15,540 --> 00:09:16,899
spray some on me, too.

167
00:09:16,900 --> 00:09:17,630
Sure.

168
00:09:17,830 --> 00:09:18,860
Here, look.

169
00:09:20,070 --> 00:09:20,940
That's enough.

170
00:09:21,900 --> 00:09:23,030
Song Cong, do you want some?

171
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,060
I'll do it myself.

172
00:09:24,070 --> 00:09:24,740
Alright.

173
00:09:24,870 --> 00:09:25,820
Thanks.

174
00:09:26,070 --> 00:09:26,989
Alright, students,

175
00:09:26,990 --> 00:09:27,989
your room keys are ready.

176
00:09:27,990 --> 00:09:29,190
Let me do a roll call.

177
00:09:29,350 --> 00:09:30,379
Chen Huan'er.

178
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:31,309
Here.

179
00:09:31,310 --> 00:09:32,310
Liao Xinyan.

180
00:09:32,660 --> 00:09:34,150
Okay, you two are sharing a room.

181
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:35,800
There was one more person
who came later.

182
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:36,390
Qi Qi.

183
00:09:36,470 --> 00:09:37,700
You'll have a room to yourself.

184
00:09:40,380 --> 00:09:40,829
Sir,

185
00:09:40,830 --> 00:09:41,739
what about us?

186
00:09:41,740 --> 00:09:42,829
Come with me for a moment.

187
00:09:42,830 --> 00:09:43,940
Qi Qi.

188
00:09:44,110 --> 00:09:45,469
If you don't mind,

189
00:09:45,470 --> 00:09:46,980
you can share a bed with me.

190
00:09:47,500 --> 00:09:49,390
It's fine, let's just go
with the arrangement.

191
00:09:49,470 --> 00:09:50,580
Don't be like that.

192
00:09:50,740 --> 00:09:52,259
I really didn't know you were coming.

193
00:09:52,260 --> 00:09:53,510
How about this,

194
00:09:53,780 --> 00:09:55,740
you take the bed,
and I'll sleep on the floor.

195
00:09:56,260 --> 00:09:58,060
No need, I can stay alone.

196
00:09:58,590 --> 00:09:59,899
Come on, let's share a room.

197
00:09:59,900 --> 00:10:00,779
Don't be shy.

198
00:10:00,780 --> 00:10:03,510
Actually, you two can take the bed,
and I'll take the floor.

199
00:10:03,620 --> 00:10:05,310
I roll onto the floor
in my sleep anyway.

200
00:10:07,190 --> 00:10:10,310
Let's stay together, please...

201
00:10:11,230 --> 00:10:12,310
Alright then.

202
00:10:12,780 --> 00:10:13,109
Okay.

203
00:10:13,110 --> 00:10:14,340
Song Cong, mosquito repellent.

204
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:16,419
I'll put it here.

205
00:10:16,420 --> 00:10:17,220
Thanks.

206
00:10:19,100 --> 00:10:20,890
Looks like everyone else
is heading that way.

207
00:10:20,900 --> 00:10:21,510
Let's go.

208
00:10:21,510 --> 00:10:22,100
Yeah, let's go.

209
00:10:22,110 --> 00:10:22,949
Thanks, sir.

210
00:10:22,950 --> 00:10:23,700
You're welcome.

211
00:10:23,820 --> 00:10:24,790
We're sharing a room.

212
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:32,790
What are you looking at?

213
00:10:33,660 --> 00:10:35,060
I feel like

214
00:10:35,350 --> 00:10:36,860
there's some tension between them.

215
00:10:38,070 --> 00:10:39,060
Tension?

216
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:42,510
Stop making things up.

217
00:10:42,540 --> 00:10:43,390
You don't understand.

218
00:10:43,710 --> 00:10:44,419
Girls

219
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:46,390
do everything holding hands.

220
00:10:47,260 --> 00:10:48,510
What? Are you jealous?

221
00:11:03,830 --> 00:11:05,220
Finally, we're at the park.

222
00:11:05,460 --> 00:11:06,730
What is this, an study trip?

223
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:08,340
We've been learning all day.

224
00:11:08,380 --> 00:11:09,619
Compared to school,

225
00:11:09,620 --> 00:11:10,700
this isn't much fun either.

226
00:11:13,950 --> 00:11:15,190
Hey, there are boats.

227
00:11:15,590 --> 00:11:17,270
Wouldn't it be fun to go boating?

228
00:11:17,990 --> 00:11:19,739
Let's pair up and race.

229
00:11:19,740 --> 00:11:20,820
That'll be even better.

230
00:11:21,070 --> 00:11:22,829
I'm not feeling well today.

231
00:11:22,830 --> 00:11:24,030
I'll team up with Huan'er.

232
00:11:24,990 --> 00:11:25,740
Huan'er...

233
00:11:30,590 --> 00:11:32,619
How about mixed-gender teams?

234
00:11:32,620 --> 00:11:34,069
That way, it'll be safer.

235
00:11:34,070 --> 00:11:35,190
Sounds good.

236
00:11:36,590 --> 00:11:37,430
Xinyan,

237
00:11:37,580 --> 00:11:38,770
since you're not feeling well,

238
00:11:38,780 --> 00:11:40,019
you team up with Jing Xichi.

239
00:11:40,020 --> 00:11:41,150
He's a sportsman.

240
00:11:42,230 --> 00:11:42,949
Qi Qi,

241
00:11:42,950 --> 00:11:44,980
you team up with Song Cong.

242
00:11:45,190 --> 00:11:45,910
Is that okay?

243
00:11:47,830 --> 00:11:48,740
What about you?

244
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:49,940
Me?

245
00:11:50,590 --> 00:11:51,829
I'll be a one-person team.

246
00:11:51,830 --> 00:11:52,899
I can take you all on

247
00:11:52,900 --> 00:11:53,860
by myself.

248
00:11:54,190 --> 00:11:54,820
Let's go.

249
00:11:55,380 --> 00:11:57,419
Chen Huan'er, you think you're so tough?

250
00:11:57,420 --> 00:11:58,320
I'm going to crush you.

251
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:58,800
Hurry up!

252
00:12:08,110 --> 00:12:09,150
Jing Xichi,

253
00:12:09,500 --> 00:12:11,659
what do you like to do
in your free time?

254
00:12:11,660 --> 00:12:12,790
Winning, of course.

255
00:12:13,070 --> 00:12:13,829
Paddle harder.

256
00:12:13,830 --> 00:12:15,060
Come on, catch up to her.

257
00:12:17,830 --> 00:12:19,460
I'm coming for you, Chen Huan'er.

258
00:12:19,620 --> 00:12:22,030
Let's just go at a steady pace.

259
00:12:22,710 --> 00:12:23,419
Safety first.

260
00:12:23,420 --> 00:12:24,670
No need to compete with them.

261
00:12:34,470 --> 00:12:35,670
Chen Huan'er.

262
00:12:35,740 --> 00:12:36,940
I'm coming for you!

263
00:12:37,260 --> 00:12:38,150
Don't run!

264
00:12:38,950 --> 00:12:39,910
Come at me.

265
00:12:41,230 --> 00:12:42,510
Come on, pedal harder.

266
00:12:42,590 --> 00:12:43,910
We're catching up...

267
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:47,550
No!

268
00:12:48,870 --> 00:12:49,740
Chen Huan'er!

269
00:12:50,110 --> 00:12:50,860
Huan'er!

270
00:12:53,660 --> 00:12:54,390
Huan'er!

271
00:12:54,950 --> 00:12:56,220
- Huan'er!
- Huan'er!

272
00:12:56,740 --> 00:12:57,670
Climb onboard.

273
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:03,100
Are you okay?

274
00:13:03,190 --> 00:13:04,390
Huan'er, how are you?

275
00:13:04,470 --> 00:13:05,270
Are you alright?

276
00:13:10,140 --> 00:13:11,550
I swallowed too much water.

277
00:13:18,500 --> 00:13:19,460
Are you okay?

278
00:13:20,070 --> 00:13:20,589
How are you?

279
00:13:20,590 --> 00:13:21,790
I'm fine.

280
00:13:22,740 --> 00:13:24,589
You should take Huan'er
back to her room.

281
00:13:24,590 --> 00:13:26,229
She's definitely caught a chill.

282
00:13:26,230 --> 00:13:27,580
I'll go buy her some cold medicine.

283
00:13:28,830 --> 00:13:30,220
Thanks, Qi Qi.

284
00:13:30,540 --> 00:13:31,139
You're welcome.

285
00:13:31,140 --> 00:13:31,940
Go on.

286
00:13:35,830 --> 00:13:36,670
Qi Qi.

287
00:13:37,020 --> 00:13:37,980
Where are you going?

288
00:13:38,420 --> 00:13:40,630
I'm going to buy medicine for Huan'er.

289
00:13:41,020 --> 00:13:42,229
I'll go with you.

290
00:13:42,230 --> 00:13:42,820
No thanks.

291
00:13:43,070 --> 00:13:44,220
I can go by myself.

292
00:13:45,470 --> 00:13:46,539
Jing Xichi,

293
00:13:46,540 --> 00:13:48,340
you were too competitive earlier.

294
00:13:48,590 --> 00:13:50,100
Good thing Huan'er knows how to swim.

295
00:13:52,350 --> 00:13:54,190
I didn't mean for that to happen.

296
00:13:55,590 --> 00:13:56,539
How about

297
00:13:56,540 --> 00:13:58,060
I go apologize to her?

298
00:13:58,710 --> 00:13:59,910
Then hurry up.

299
00:14:00,470 --> 00:14:01,510
Alright, I'll go.

300
00:14:06,740 --> 00:14:07,700
Song Cong.

301
00:14:08,780 --> 00:14:10,510
Do you know where the pharmacy is?

302
00:14:11,070 --> 00:14:11,899
Next to the hotel.

303
00:14:11,900 --> 00:14:13,019
There's a busy street there.

304
00:14:13,020 --> 00:14:14,030
Should be one there.

305
00:14:15,310 --> 00:14:16,790
Can you take me there?

306
00:14:16,990 --> 00:14:18,340
I don't know the way.

307
00:14:18,900 --> 00:14:19,739
Well...

308
00:14:19,740 --> 00:14:21,740
Why don't you ask the front desk?

309
00:14:21,950 --> 00:14:23,060
I've got something to do.

310
00:14:23,710 --> 00:14:24,270
Okay.

311
00:14:56,990 --> 00:14:59,030
Song Cong, try one.

312
00:15:00,260 --> 00:15:01,430
I've had it before.

313
00:15:07,950 --> 00:15:09,670
Let's have a hug too.

314
00:15:30,540 --> 00:15:31,829
What are you doing?

315
00:15:31,830 --> 00:15:32,700
Why are you out here?

316
00:15:33,070 --> 00:15:34,190
You might catch a cold.

317
00:15:35,900 --> 00:15:37,630
I just took a hot shower.

318
00:15:37,990 --> 00:15:38,980
I'm feeling warm.

319
00:15:40,420 --> 00:15:41,220
Where's Xinyan?

320
00:15:41,780 --> 00:15:43,510
She just had dinner with me.

321
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:47,379
But she was chatting
with the club members.

322
00:15:47,380 --> 00:15:48,989
I didn't feel like I had much to say,

323
00:15:48,990 --> 00:15:50,270
so I left.

324
00:15:55,870 --> 00:15:56,550
Here,

325
00:15:56,620 --> 00:15:57,630
I bought these for you.

326
00:15:58,660 --> 00:16:00,100
Why did you buy oranges?

327
00:16:00,990 --> 00:16:02,190
I wanted to apologize to you.

328
00:16:04,540 --> 00:16:05,340
You see,

329
00:16:06,590 --> 00:16:08,190
when we were boating earlier,

330
00:16:08,950 --> 00:16:10,220
I went overboard.

331
00:16:11,500 --> 00:16:12,390
I'm sorry.

332
00:16:16,870 --> 00:16:17,820
It's okay.

333
00:16:20,710 --> 00:16:22,510
If anyone should apologize,

334
00:16:23,070 --> 00:16:25,190
it should be me.

335
00:16:28,070 --> 00:16:29,259
I wasn't thinking clearly

336
00:16:29,260 --> 00:16:30,790
back at the park earlier.

337
00:16:31,470 --> 00:16:33,310
I ended up splitting you and Qi Qi up.

338
00:16:34,950 --> 00:16:36,740
Xichi, I'm sorry.

339
00:16:37,020 --> 00:16:38,430
I'm really sorry.

340
00:16:39,070 --> 00:16:40,189
What are you saying?

341
00:16:40,190 --> 00:16:41,430
Just eat your orange.

342
00:16:41,710 --> 00:16:42,740
Listen,

343
00:16:43,070 --> 00:16:44,700
these oranges are really good.

344
00:16:44,990 --> 00:16:46,499
You haven't even tasted them yet.

345
00:16:46,500 --> 00:16:48,229
They're full of vitamin C,

346
00:16:48,230 --> 00:16:49,379
and they help prevent colds.

347
00:16:49,380 --> 00:16:50,469
You mustn't get sick now.

348
00:16:50,470 --> 00:16:51,820
I'm perfectly healthy.

349
00:16:51,830 --> 00:16:53,060
I run every day,

350
00:16:53,310 --> 00:16:54,790
and my dad teaches me martial arts.

351
00:16:55,260 --> 00:16:57,030
Here it goes, I wonder if it's sweet.

352
00:16:57,260 --> 00:16:58,190
You go first.

353
00:16:58,350 --> 00:16:59,030
Eat mine.

354
00:16:59,380 --> 00:17:00,740
It's too big.

355
00:17:01,380 --> 00:17:02,310
Try it.

356
00:17:04,270 --> 00:17:05,789
Why are you throwing it at me?

357
00:17:05,790 --> 00:17:06,780
Just taste it, come on.

358
00:17:08,320 --> 00:17:10,580
(Red date ginger tea)
Wow, I picked some good oranges.

359
00:17:10,590 --> 00:17:11,379
You ate it.

360
00:17:11,380 --> 00:17:12,029
Fine, I'll stop.

361
00:17:12,030 --> 00:17:12,640
You eat it.

362
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:13,790
You have a cold, so you eat it.

363
00:17:13,980 --> 00:17:14,620
Here, eat it.

364
00:17:14,620 --> 00:17:15,380
I don't want to.

365
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:15,800
Eat it...

366
00:17:15,800 --> 00:17:17,400
I don't like oranges, but you do.

367
00:17:19,580 --> 00:17:23,020
♪Look at the planet on your left♪

368
00:17:24,110 --> 00:17:25,300
(Since that day,)

369
00:17:25,900 --> 00:17:28,109
(I don't know if we became)

370
00:17:28,110 --> 00:17:30,500
(Donghai Tianhe Travel Bus)
(closer or more distant.)

371
00:17:32,220 --> 00:17:35,350
(It seemed like everyone had something
on their mind.)

372
00:17:36,550 --> 00:17:38,070
(But back then,)

373
00:17:38,700 --> 00:17:41,110
(I didn't notice it at all.)

374
00:17:43,980 --> 00:17:47,100
♪Alone when I drift♪

375
00:17:47,460 --> 00:17:52,780
♪I dreamed about you all night♪

376
00:17:54,740 --> 00:18:01,900
♪You can see me so deep inside♪

377
00:18:02,020 --> 00:18:05,820
♪So deep inside♪

378
00:18:06,580 --> 00:18:09,780
♪Deep inside♪

379
00:18:13,860 --> 00:18:18,660
(Donghai Tianhe Travel Bus Co., Ltd.)

380
00:18:34,140 --> 00:18:36,110
Didn't you cry about wanting to go?

381
00:18:36,140 --> 00:18:37,740
Why do you look like this coming back?

382
00:18:37,750 --> 00:18:38,910
Didn't have fun?

383
00:18:41,140 --> 00:18:42,110
It was great,

384
00:18:42,420 --> 00:18:43,390
just a bit tiring.

385
00:18:44,030 --> 00:18:45,459
Then rest well tonight.

386
00:18:45,460 --> 00:18:47,350
Tomorrow, get back
to studying seriously.

387
00:18:47,550 --> 00:18:48,940
Don't forget your promise.

388
00:18:49,110 --> 00:18:50,300
If I let you go,

389
00:18:50,350 --> 00:18:52,390
you'll make it into the top ten
next semester.

390
00:18:53,830 --> 00:18:54,670
Alright.

391
00:19:06,420 --> 00:19:10,260
(The Fountainhead)

392
00:19:27,750 --> 00:19:28,830
Hey, old friend.

393
00:19:29,200 --> 00:19:31,100
I'm not wearing the summer uniform
because I

394
00:19:31,110 --> 00:19:32,070
haven't collected it.

395
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:33,630
Why aren't you wearing yours?

396
00:19:36,510 --> 00:19:37,939
Uniforms are meant to make

397
00:19:37,940 --> 00:19:40,070
everyone look the same.

398
00:19:40,380 --> 00:19:41,910
They erase individuality.

399
00:19:42,140 --> 00:19:43,390
I don't want to wear it.

400
00:19:50,700 --> 00:19:51,780
A kindred spirit, huh?

401
00:20:09,380 --> 00:20:11,390
(Did everyone get home safely?)

402
00:20:19,380 --> 00:20:21,220
(I'm about to sleep.)

403
00:20:21,420 --> 00:20:23,980
(Rest early, everyone.)

404
00:20:32,860 --> 00:20:37,220
(Did everyone get home safely?
Rest early, everyone.)

405
00:20:40,620 --> 00:20:41,419
You already ate it.

406
00:20:41,420 --> 00:20:42,069
Okay, I'll stop.

407
00:20:42,070 --> 00:20:42,789
You eat it.

408
00:20:42,790 --> 00:20:43,939
You're the one with a cold.

409
00:20:43,940 --> 00:20:44,459
You eat it.

410
00:20:44,460 --> 00:20:45,540
I don't want to.

411
00:20:49,420 --> 00:20:51,459
(Did everyone get home safely?
I'm about to sleep.)

412
00:20:51,460 --> 00:20:53,350
(Okay, good night.)

413
00:21:10,380 --> 00:21:12,789
(Rest early, everyone.
Okay, good night.)

414
00:21:12,790 --> 00:21:13,700
(Good night.)

415
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:23,180
(Okay, good night. Good night.)

416
00:21:38,100 --> 00:21:41,380
(Tianhe No. 1 Middle School)

417
00:21:46,700 --> 00:21:47,460
Qi Qi.

418
00:21:48,550 --> 00:21:49,300
Qi Qi.

419
00:21:51,070 --> 00:21:51,780
Qi Qi.

420
00:21:52,660 --> 00:21:54,900
I finally see you. I tried
calling you over the holidays,

421
00:21:54,940 --> 00:21:55,900
but you never came out.

422
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:56,860
After that trip,

423
00:21:56,870 --> 00:21:58,350
I was stuck in tutoring classes.

424
00:21:59,590 --> 00:22:00,780
How are you guys?

425
00:22:02,380 --> 00:22:03,350
The three of us?

426
00:22:03,830 --> 00:22:05,630
We're good. Just the same as always.

427
00:22:05,660 --> 00:22:06,350
That's good.

428
00:22:08,440 --> 00:22:10,780
Why do I get the feeling
you've become colder toward Qi Qi

429
00:22:10,790 --> 00:22:12,540
after the holidays?

430
00:22:16,900 --> 00:22:17,910
I realized

431
00:22:18,350 --> 00:22:20,390
that I'm a rare soul.

432
00:22:21,260 --> 00:22:22,410
The fact that I'm so noble

433
00:22:22,420 --> 00:22:23,419
makes it impossible

434
00:22:23,420 --> 00:22:25,150
for me to truly connect with anyone.

435
00:22:25,780 --> 00:22:26,980
You wouldn't understand.

436
00:22:28,180 --> 00:22:29,150
Sure.

437
00:22:29,380 --> 00:22:30,109
By the way,

438
00:22:30,110 --> 00:22:32,540
I forgot to ask which floor
the humanities class is on.

439
00:22:32,940 --> 00:22:35,029
They moved us to another building.

440
00:22:35,030 --> 00:22:36,740
They say it's to facilitate management.

441
00:22:38,750 --> 00:22:39,460
Alright then.

442
00:22:39,590 --> 00:22:40,419
I'll just run faster

443
00:22:40,420 --> 00:22:41,780
and visit you during breaks.

444
00:22:42,270 --> 00:22:43,219
I'll visit you too.

445
00:22:43,220 --> 00:22:45,000
Let's go to that snack stall
after school.

446
00:22:45,180 --> 00:22:45,659
Yes!

447
00:22:45,660 --> 00:22:47,309
Alright, stop with the emotional moment.

448
00:22:47,310 --> 00:22:48,700
Morning self-study is starting.

449
00:22:49,030 --> 00:22:50,070
Ignore him.

450
00:22:50,620 --> 00:22:52,150
We'll never be apart.

451
00:22:55,140 --> 00:22:56,500
You're heading this way?

452
00:22:57,620 --> 00:22:58,670
Alright, I'm off.

453
00:22:59,030 --> 00:23:00,350
Wait for me after class.

454
00:23:00,510 --> 00:23:01,190
Bye.

455
00:23:01,270 --> 00:23:02,390
I'll come to find you.

456
00:23:10,140 --> 00:23:11,980
Wait up, Jing Xichi!

457
00:23:13,270 --> 00:23:13,829
I said

458
00:23:13,830 --> 00:23:14,619
wait up.

459
00:23:14,620 --> 00:23:15,590
Chen Huan'er!

460
00:23:24,180 --> 00:23:25,830
That's all for today's lesson.

461
00:23:26,180 --> 00:23:27,110
Class dismissed.

462
00:23:30,060 --> 00:23:31,480
(I conducted precise calculations.)

463
00:23:31,480 --> 00:23:33,290
(As soon as the bell rings,
I sprint outside,)

464
00:23:33,290 --> 00:23:34,460
(following the planned route,)

465
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:36,700
(down three floors, across campus
to the art building,)

466
00:23:36,700 --> 00:23:38,420
(up two floors to reach
Qi Qi's classroom.)

467
00:23:38,420 --> 00:23:39,860
(Say five sentences, then rush back.)

468
00:23:39,870 --> 00:23:40,980
(This way, I won't be late.)

469
00:23:41,030 --> 00:23:41,699
(Two conditions)

470
00:23:41,700 --> 00:23:43,419
(must be met in order for us
to meet up.)

471
00:23:43,420 --> 00:23:45,680
(Qi Qi and I must strictly control
our speaking speed)

472
00:23:45,700 --> 00:23:46,860
(and sentence length.)

473
00:23:46,870 --> 00:23:48,419
(And there can be no bathroom breaks,)

474
00:23:48,420 --> 00:23:50,020
(getting water, discussing problems,)

475
00:23:50,110 --> 00:23:51,260
(or any other distractions.)

476
00:23:52,310 --> 00:23:53,390
Huan'er!

477
00:23:53,590 --> 00:23:54,540
Qi Qi!

478
00:23:56,220 --> 00:23:57,260
Slow down.

479
00:23:57,700 --> 00:23:58,509
How's it going?

480
00:23:58,510 --> 00:24:00,619
Are you getting used
to the art class?

481
00:24:00,620 --> 00:24:02,179
I'm fine. How about you?

482
00:24:02,180 --> 00:24:03,219
How have you been?

483
00:24:03,220 --> 00:24:03,789
Tired?

484
00:24:03,790 --> 00:24:06,190
I'm alright. Same as before.

485
00:24:08,980 --> 00:24:10,070
So soon?

486
00:24:10,140 --> 00:24:11,939
I'll come to find you
after school, okay?

487
00:24:11,940 --> 00:24:13,220
Hurry back to class.

488
00:24:17,830 --> 00:24:19,070
Go on...

489
00:24:27,900 --> 00:24:29,829
(Actually, deep down, I know)

490
00:24:29,830 --> 00:24:32,390
(these brief meetings
are more symbolic than practical.)

491
00:24:32,510 --> 00:24:33,749
(Class meetings, quizzes...)

492
00:24:33,750 --> 00:24:35,549
(There will always be
more important things)

493
00:24:35,550 --> 00:24:37,430
(than a fleeting conversation.)

494
00:24:37,750 --> 00:24:39,190
(But I still want to prove)

495
00:24:39,510 --> 00:24:40,780
(that we haven't drifted apart.)

496
00:24:43,790 --> 00:24:44,940
So tired...

497
00:24:47,220 --> 00:24:48,939
Everyone, quiet down.

498
00:24:48,940 --> 00:24:50,500
Mr. Xu is in a meeting.

499
00:24:50,620 --> 00:24:51,830
Class will start later.

500
00:24:51,940 --> 00:24:52,749
While we wait,

501
00:24:52,750 --> 00:24:53,349
I have

502
00:24:53,350 --> 00:24:54,699
an announcement.

503
00:24:54,700 --> 00:24:57,070
There will be a talent show
this semester.

504
00:24:57,350 --> 00:24:59,070
Every class must prepare a performance.

505
00:24:59,270 --> 00:25:00,589
Who wants to sign up?

506
00:25:00,590 --> 00:25:02,029
- Not me.
- Not me.

507
00:25:02,030 --> 00:25:03,590
Who has the time for this?

508
00:25:04,980 --> 00:25:07,220
I know everyone is busy with school.

509
00:25:07,420 --> 00:25:09,979
How about we keep it simple?

510
00:25:09,980 --> 00:25:11,269
Let's do a poetry recital.

511
00:25:11,270 --> 00:25:13,789
Another poetry recital?

512
00:25:13,790 --> 00:25:14,940
How boring.

513
00:25:15,310 --> 00:25:16,309
Xinyan!

514
00:25:16,310 --> 00:25:17,300
Xinyan!

515
00:25:17,550 --> 00:25:19,110
I think a poetry recital is fine.

516
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:21,340
Song Cong will do it.

517
00:25:21,350 --> 00:25:22,150
Not me.

518
00:25:22,310 --> 00:25:23,179
Why not?

519
00:25:23,180 --> 00:25:24,069
Why would I do it?

520
00:25:24,070 --> 00:25:25,109
You're perfect for it.

521
00:25:25,110 --> 00:25:26,309
No, I'm not.

522
00:25:26,310 --> 00:25:29,379
How about letting Jing Xichi
do some freestyle football tricks?

523
00:25:29,380 --> 00:25:31,110
At least it won't be as boring.

524
00:25:31,140 --> 00:25:32,979
Good idea...

525
00:25:32,980 --> 00:25:33,749
I'm not doing it.

526
00:25:33,750 --> 00:25:34,219
Please.

527
00:25:34,220 --> 00:25:34,789
No.

528
00:25:34,790 --> 00:25:36,269
Just him doing tricks alone

529
00:25:36,270 --> 00:25:37,500
is pretty dull.

530
00:25:37,510 --> 00:25:39,670
Right? It's boring. I'm out.

531
00:25:39,700 --> 00:25:40,789
How about we get

532
00:25:40,790 --> 00:25:42,459
some of the girls from the aerobics team

533
00:25:42,460 --> 00:25:43,749
to be cheerleaders?

534
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:45,500
That way, it becomes a full act.

535
00:25:45,900 --> 00:25:46,749
Why don't you do it?

536
00:25:46,750 --> 00:25:48,419
You're good at organizing.

537
00:25:48,420 --> 00:25:49,549
Back when we asked everyone

538
00:25:49,550 --> 00:25:50,659
to join the sports day,,

539
00:25:50,660 --> 00:25:51,789
weren't you the one saying

540
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:53,500
we need team spirit?

541
00:25:53,700 --> 00:25:55,029
I think this works.

542
00:25:55,030 --> 00:25:56,960
If there's no other idea,
let's go with this.

543
00:25:57,020 --> 00:25:58,260
Sounds good...

544
00:25:58,270 --> 00:26:00,020
Xinyan!

545
00:26:00,030 --> 00:26:02,350
I'll join.

546
00:26:02,380 --> 00:26:03,390
But

547
00:26:03,750 --> 00:26:04,870
only if Song Cong joins.

548
00:26:05,030 --> 00:26:06,139
I don't even play soccer.

549
00:26:06,140 --> 00:26:07,219
You don't need to.

550
00:26:07,220 --> 00:26:08,179
Then what do I do?

551
00:26:08,180 --> 00:26:09,220
Be a cheerleader.

552
00:26:11,540 --> 00:26:13,130
You're pretty strong for a cheerleader.

553
00:26:13,140 --> 00:26:14,700
Don't drag me into this embarrassment.

554
00:26:15,030 --> 00:26:17,070
Everyone, did you hear that?

555
00:26:17,140 --> 00:26:18,869
How is participating in a group activity

556
00:26:18,870 --> 00:26:19,940
embarrassing?

557
00:26:20,140 --> 00:26:21,139
Your mindset is wrong.

558
00:26:21,140 --> 00:26:22,390
What's wrong with it?

559
00:26:22,940 --> 00:26:23,899
Think about it.

560
00:26:23,900 --> 00:26:26,040
Why do people say you're
out of touch with reality?

561
00:26:26,040 --> 00:26:28,140
Why did you transfer to our class
in the first place?

562
00:26:28,140 --> 00:26:29,080
Wasn't it because

563
00:26:29,080 --> 00:26:30,800
you wanted to join
more group activities,

564
00:26:30,800 --> 00:26:33,160
to experience a more interesting
high school life?

565
00:26:33,510 --> 00:26:34,309
Am I right?

566
00:26:34,310 --> 00:26:34,659
Yes.

567
00:26:34,660 --> 00:26:37,029
Right? So should he join or not?

568
00:26:37,030 --> 00:26:38,500
- Yes, he should.
- Yes, he should.

569
00:26:38,550 --> 00:26:39,509
Just go for it.

570
00:26:39,510 --> 00:26:40,540
