830
00:36:30,270 --> 00:36:31,110
Check your pockets.

831
00:36:33,830 --> 00:36:34,670
Take it out.

832
00:36:34,830 --> 00:36:35,780
Do you have any?

833
00:36:36,020 --> 00:36:36,829
